===Etymology 1===
From {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*krəp|t=to [[weep]]}}; cognate with {{cog|bo|ཁྲབ་ཁྲབ||[[weeper]]}} (STEDT; {{zh-ref|Mei, 1980b}}; {{zh-ref|Coblin, 1986}}; {{zh-ref|Baxter, 1995}}; {{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

Often thought to be related to {{och-l|淚|tears}} ({{zh-ref|Mei, 1980b}}; {{zh-ref|Baxter and Sagart, 2014}}), but see there for more.

